<span class="comment_time"><a href="index.html?replytocom=3#comment-16" title="Permalink to this comment" rel="nofollow">August 15, 2011 at 10:05 pm</a></span>

					</dt>
					<dd class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-16">
<p>One checklist item to address re: security is verifying that every single database call within the site&#8217;s backend is run through a sanitizer.  SQL Injection seems to be the dominant method of breaking into websites, and has been consistently effective for years.</p>
