<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-20">
<p>I&#8217;d also add FavIcons, I&#8217;ll admit, I don&#8217;t use them, however if not used, they clog up your Apache error_log and also waste server requests, plus if someone bookmarks your site, at least there&#8217;s an icon. Small yes, but I think it&#8217;s something to look out for.</p>
